OL,3,CTwo teenagers convicted of killing 17-
OL,4,Cyear-old boy in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FTwo teenagers have been convicted of
OL,7,Fkilling a "funny and polite" 17-year-
OL,8,Fold boy in Wolverhampton, following a
OL,9,Fsix-week trial.
OL,11,FHarleigh Hepworth was stabbed in the
OL,12,Fchest in West Park on 7 March. A 17-
OL,13,Fyear-old, who cannot be named for
OL,14,Flegal reasons, was found guilty of
OL,15,Fmurder and robbery.
OL,17,FA second teenager Jovarn Esterine, who
OL,18,Fwas 17 at the time but has since
OL,19,Fturned 18, was found not guilty of
OL,20,Fmurder, but guilty of manslaughter and
OL,21,Frobbery.
