OL,4,Cyear-old boy in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FHarleigh's family has released a
OL,7,Fstatement through the police, saying
OL,8,Fhe will "always be remembered".
OL,10,F"He had positive plans for his future"
OL,12,FThe statement reads: "On the 7th
OL,13,FMarch, two weeks after his 17th
OL,14,FBirthday, Harleigh had his short life
OL,15,Fended in an instant through a moment
OL,16,Fof mindless aggression.
OL,18,F"Our family, his girlfriend and close
OL,19,Ffriends will no longer be able to
OL,20,Fenjoy seeing him grow, mature and
OL,21,Fenjoy life.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
