OL,3,CTwo teenagers convicted of killing 17-
OL,4,Cyear-old boy in Wolverhampton
OL,6,F"He had positive plans for his future.
OL,7,FHarleigh had a great sense of humour,
OL,8,Fhe was funny, and he was polite.
OL,10,F"We will miss him massively, but we
OL,11,Fwill always remember his cheekiness,
OL,12,Fhis infectious smile and the fun times
OL,13,Fwe had together.
OL,15,F"Harleigh's is another young life lost
OL,16,Fbefore they had the chance to know
OL,17,Fwhat life is about."
