OL,4,Cyear-old boy in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FWest Midlands Police said Harleigh was
OL,7,Fvisiting Wolverhampton with a friend
OL,8,Fbefore they were confronted by their
OL,9,Ftwo eventual attackers, who had met
OL,10,Fthem with an "ulterior motive".
OL,12,FAfter a brief exchange, Harleigh was
OL,13,Fstabbed in the chest and ran away, but
OL,14,Fwas found lying in the park and later
OL,15,Fdied from his injuries.
