OL,4,Cyear-old boy in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FAs Harleigh was stabbed, Esterine
OL,7,Fstopped Harleigh's friend from
OL,8,Fintervening, holding a knife to his
OL,9,Fchest and threatening to kill him
OL,10,Funless he told them the passcode to
OL,11,Fhis phone which was then stolen.
OL,13,FEsterine and the 17-year-old ran away
OL,14,Fand discarded one of the stolen phones
OL,15,Fin a nearby drain.
