OL,3,CTwo teenagers convicted of killing 17-
OL,4,Cyear-old boy in Wolverhampton
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Ade George, who
OL,7,Fled the investigation, said:
OL,8,F"Throughout this case our thoughts
OL,9,Fhave always been with Harleigh's
OL,10,Ffamily who have been devastated by his
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,F"We hope that the conviction will
OL,14,Fprovide a sense of justice for the
OL,15,Funjust killing of Harleigh."
OL,17,FThe pair will be sentenced at a later
OL,18,Fdate.
